dc_title_s: Bergen County, New Jersey highways 1965 map 3
dc_description_s: Base map of Bergen County. Sheet three of an 11 plate map. Prepared by the New Jersey State Highway Department, Division of Planning in cooperation with the U. S. Department of Commerce, Bureau of Public Roads. Culture, county roads and municipal streets are as of 1953. This sheet includes a key of selected towns and their population amounts.
